arts.ttl: Preview: Lille vs. Toulouse - prediction, team news, lineups
arts.sum: Sports Mole previews Saturday's Ligue 1 clash between Lille and Toulouse, including predictions, team news and possible lineups.

The home side also had a chance to open the scoring, but Lunin produced a superb save to keep out Jonathan David's header and, after the rebound, produced a wonderful reflex save to keep the ball out and onto the post. Bellingham retrieved the ball in the 6th minute and fed to Vini Jr, who cut inside and shot at the near post, but Chevalier made a fine save.
